description:
This is the original requiem-1.0.tar.gz file, originally from the Hymn Project. It is a commandline utility for stripping Apple&amp;#039;s Fairplay DRM from iTunes tracks, and it works exceptionally well. Apple sent a C&amp;D order to the Hymn Project forums in an attempt to stop this software from spreading, and I was able to snag a copy before the links were taken down. Accept no substitutions!

